<h3 class="date"><a href="/2005/nov/04/">&#x27a0;</a> November 4, 2005</h3>


<div class="row">
    <div class="span12">


    
    <div class="well" id="10_ways_to_please_us_the_custo" >

        
        <a name="002094"></a>
        

        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.nytimes.com/2005/11/02/technology/techspecial1/02pogue.html?ex=1288587600&amp;en=5975c4bf4cb76c26&amp;ei=5090&amp;partner=rssuserland&amp;emc=rss">10 Ways to Please Us, the Customers</a></h4>

        

        <p>Excellent list from David Pogue.  &#8220;We may be the bane of your existence, but we&#8217;re also the reason for it; you&#8217;re stuck with us. We&#8217;ve got our credit cards ready - now show us some love.&#8221;</p>

